# CTA-PX Flashcards (ASCII Edition)

Cut out, print, or screenshot.

---

## Card 1 — "I’m confused"
```
O ⟂
```

## Card 2 — "Stop / Wait"
```
O ↓
```

## Card 3 — "Explain again"
```
O ↑
```

## Card 4 — "I need help"
```
O X
```

## Card 5 — "Mixed up"
```
O ~ R
```

## Card 6 — "Reset"
```
↺ O
```

## Card 7 — "All good"
```
(O→R→S)
```

## Card 8 — "I need space"
```
O ←
```

## Card 9 — "I’m ready again"
```
→ O
```

## Card 10 — "We’re almost ok"
```
O_
```
